   The XILS 3 LE  is an exciting new matrix style virtual modular synthesizer. 
   Based on the architecture  of the legendary EMS  VCS3 synth, the XILS  3 is 
   capable of creating both 'classic' sounds and totally new ones. 
             
             
   The  XILS  3's  matrix  design  is  capable  of  more  than  450 connection 
   permutations,   offering  more   routing  possibilities   than  any   other 
   commercially available virtual synthesizer. 
             
   In addition, a built-in sequencer, based  on the EMS 256 sequencer, can  be 
   used to create original and complex sequences. 
             
             
   The XILS 3 LE comes with hundreds of presets that provide instant access to 
   a broad  range of  sounds  and  styles ranging  from modern  electronica to 
   classic 1970s retro and experimental.  You can also program it  yourself to 
   create your own unique sounds!
